snippet.title: Eggstraction - Official Trailer (Coming Spring 2024)
snippet.description:
🐔 WISHLIST NOW: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2355860/Eggstraction/

Eggstraction is a multiplayer (4vs1) party game where four feathered friends must face off against an egg-napping farmer. 

With chaos around every corner, can the chickens rescue their stolen eggs, or will they end up back in their cage? 

Thank you for all the support!

#eggstraction #indiegame #chicken #trailer
